+# Loop controls
+
+KaltraSounds beta.7 adds shared loop controls for native regions, WorldGuard/RedProtect regions, and biome loops.
+
+```yaml
+Loop:
+  Enabled: true
+  Delay: 0
+  Period: 100
+  Period Randomness: 0
+  Maximum Plays: 0
+
+  Fade In:
+    Enabled: false
+    Plays: 3
+    Start Volume Multiplier: 0.2
+    Curve: SMOOTHSTEP
+
+  Stop On Exit:
+    Enabled: true
+    Delay: 0
+    Fade Out:
+      Enabled: false
+      Plays